？影響差幾遠又點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期六日或者夜晚掛8仔/紅黑雨係咪真係會鬆手d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面果兩幅圖又應該點正確解讀呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咁多疑問又想知道答案既巴絲有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登氣象台三位巴打將會係黎緊星期六為大家一一解答，其中一位巴打仲曾經為香港天文台工作，到時會分享工作點滴同天文台既有趣小秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中包括香港天文台內部點睇澳門果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n很想要吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家就快d去報名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 名額有限，full左就唔知幾時再有機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9840c2bb3742cc92fb8ab0726c3165e9be96b4b9","tid":449250,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/31/003546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F003546_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b342c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港又打風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/31/003444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F003444_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff0f1782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咪玩啦去越南架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解個風超強但香港得1號波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解明明個風行得離香港咁遠又會8號波而且真係幾大風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日聽到東登西登又係咩黎？東登定西登對香港有幾重要？影響差幾遠又點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期六日或者夜晚掛8仔/紅黑雨係咪真係會鬆手d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面果兩幅圖又應該點正確解讀呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咁多疑問又想知道答案既巴絲有福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登氣象台三位巴打將會係黎緊星期六為大家一一解答，其中一位巴打仲曾經為香港天文台工作，到時會分享工作點滴同天文台既有趣小秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中包括香港天文台內部點睇澳門果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n很想要吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家就快d去報名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 名額有限，full左就唔知幾時再有機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51541b5df90623088261f0cfba77cb31c694676b","tid":449250,"uid":44630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11月都打風？　菲以東現低壓區稍後進入南海<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fbkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b2bf55c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031115249272-1031_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[quote]秋意漸深，但天文台九天天氣預報指出，菲律賓以東海域出現低壓區，並會在本周後期進入南海中至南部。台灣中央氣象局亦指，位於南海及菲律賓以東海面的熱帶擾動，未來不排除有進一步發展的可能。莫非11月還會打風？ <br />\n<br />\n另外，香港天文台資料顯示，對上一次11月份有颱風吹襲香港，已是2013年11月1日，當時強颱風「羅莎」吹襲，天文台發出1號戒備信號。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n竟然真係有報紙吹奏呢個武雷宮咁遠既會打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n報紙佬係咪認為入南海就一定關香港事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n天文台會講離香港1000公里外既南海南部多多少少係因為畀行船既睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想以後自己唔再畀報紙佬呃識得自己睇會唔會打風，各位就要黎學野捧場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852e38cec712ea1e9d5fa222e38e69c6cabf0609","tid":449250,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"淨係話我知幾點掛八號風球就得"},{"pid":"31b2415a970e3249f757fa48b9e0ecdc0d913784","tid":449250,"uid":123583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係話我知幾點掛八號風球就得</blockquote><br />\n你黎睇睇，明左點樣先會出8號波之後，唔洗再靠人，你都可以大約估到幾時會8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af40a2f539fc70c4f6204563608982d61c03492","tid":449250,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e70ec6ba3c4975bd876e320b382d9dd7a31eb9c","tid":449250,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6501853deeb863647224cba649dbf7b44a4accc4","tid":449250,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"星期六唔得閒，我期待咗好耐架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eae932d93d46995fd190ed72e24f04d345bc7a","tid":449250,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:34:51.000Z","msg